s=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再次緊急召集，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期一 (8月12日晚) ！！！</span></span>🆘🆘🆘🆘🆘🆘<br />\n所有人再歸位‼️‼️<br />\n集合3至5萬人,<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jffMH3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjffMH3E.png&h=f9c0063d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">檢舉&quot;仇恨言論&quot;！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymYeRW7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymYeRW7.png&h=814e30aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n22:00 FB,發動集體檢舉<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;向香港警察致敬&quot;</span>專頁,5分鐘後 重複檢舉一次 ,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSaluteToHKPolice%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ52o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=b72fb3cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/</a><br />\n<br />\n22:15 集體檢舉<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;HKG報&quot;</span> ,5分鐘後大家再檢舉一次,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkgpaocom/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkgpaocom%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ52o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=be22c56e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkgpaocom/</a><br />\n<br />\n22:30 ,檢舉<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;幫港出聲&quot;</span>專頁,5分鐘後再檢舉多次,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilentmajorityhk%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ52o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=e0e1502a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silentmajorityhk/</a><br />\n<br />\n22:45 ,檢舉<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;港人揮手區&quot;</span>專頁,5分鐘後再檢舉多次,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PeopleOfHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPeopleOfHK%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ52o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=6005206c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PeopleOfHK/</a> <br />\n<br />\n大家用 whatspp ,IG ,snapchat...等分享比朋友又好,口講又好,有Facebook既,應該要幫手檢舉! 增加對家文宣成本,我地香港人唔會屈服同認輸,大家請盡量分享出去~每人分享比10至20個朋友,記得晚上10點開始Facebook 集體檢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">上面4個係基本盤<br />\n<br />\n下面亦有DLC支線任免費俾唔夠喉既手足繼續玩！(遲d都會為佢地輪流發起每晚檢舉嘉年華)</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥沒有一個是無辜的🔥<br />\n如果大家嘅憤怒仲未平息，請繼續順序重覆Facebook 檢舉步驟❗❗❗<br />\n<br />\n😡除暴安良大聯盟<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%99%A4%E6%9A%B4%E5%AE%89%E8%89%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-106159104055088/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-106159104055088%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ52o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=41ce7906\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%99%A4%E6%9A%B4%E5%AE%89%E8%89%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-106159104055088/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n😡時聞香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/HongKongGoodNews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FHongKongGoodNews%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ52o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=331ae09f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/HongKongGoodNews/</a><br />\n<br />\n😡咩議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E5%92%A9%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-1999082133720871/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E5%2592%25A9%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1-1999082133720871%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ52o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=538732ea\" target=\"_blank\">h